OL,3,CMan arrested after 'doing a runner'
OL,4,Cfrom ambulance
OL,6,FThe officer has been inundated with
OL,7,Fcalls to take up rugby after GMP
OL,8,FTraffic posted this video on social
OL,9,Fmedia
OL,11,FA suspected motorbike thief has been
OL,12,Farrested after he made a run from it
OL,13,Ffrom the back of an ambulance he was
OL,14,Fbeing treated in after he crashed.
OL,16,F(GMP) was called to Whitworth Road in
OL,17,FRochdale at 2:30pm on Thursday 9 May.
