OL,3,CMan arrested after 'doing a runner'
OL,4,Cfrom ambulance
OL,6,FIn footage posted on social media,
OL,7,Fofficers went to the ambulance to
OL,8,Farrest the suspect, who is then seeing
OL,9,Fjumping out of the ambulance, and
OL,10,Frunning down the road before being
OL,11,Farrested in what some people have
OL,12,Fdescribed as a 'rugby tackle' which
OL,13,Fleads to both the suspect and police
OL,14,Fofficer rolling over in the road.
OL,16,FThe man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,17,Fof theft of a motor vehicle,
OL,18,Fpossession of drugs and an offensive
OL,19,Fweapon, and escaping lawful custody.
