OL,3,CMan arrested after 'doing a runner'
OL,4,Cfrom ambulance
OL,6,FThe social media footage has prompted
OL,7,Flots of calls for the arresting
OL,8,Fofficer to try out for a rugby club,
OL,9,Fwith one woman suggesting he should
OL,10,Fplay for the England team, saying "we
OL,11,Fmight win a game then".
OL,13,FOne comment described it as a "high
OL,14,Ftackle" and said the officer should be
OL,15,Fput in the sin bin.
OL,17,FGMP's Traffic unit's tongue in cheek
OL,18,Fresponse was "A fine of cream cakes
OL,19,Fshould suffice! And he split his
OL,20,Fpants..."
